           ≡⟨ cong (e (insertClockCtx i κ Δ')) (sym (Ctx.MorComp Γ)) ⟩
             e (insertClockCtx i κ Δ') (Ctx.Mor Γ Δ _ x)
           ≡⟨ cong (e (insertClockCtx i κ Δ')) (Ctx.MorComp Γ) ⟩
             e (insertClockCtx i κ Δ')
               (Ctx.Mor Γ Δ' _
                 (Ctx.Mor Γ Δ Δ' x))
           ∎
         ))
